Griffon ships with a few convenience targets such as [create-mvc|commandLine], [create-script|commandLine] and so on that will create [Controllers|guide:8. Controllers] and different artifact types for you.
{note}
These are merely for your convenience and you can just as easily use an IDE or your favorite text editor.
{note}

There are many such @create-*@ commands that can be explored in the command line reference guide.